COMMENTS
The Weeknd and Bella Hadid attends "Manus x Machina: Fashion In An Age Of Technology" Costume Institute Gala at Metropolitan Museum of Art on May 2, 2016 in New York City.
KevinMazur/WireImage
Among the flashy spectacles at Monday night's 2016 Met Gala ball was a most unexpected sight:Nas joining The Weeknd for a rare live performance of the remix version of the Canadian crooner's 2015 track "Tell Your Friends."2016 Met Gala Red Carpet Photos: Taylor Swift & More!The Weeknd, attending with girlfriend Bella Hadid, performed his hit "The Hills" at the soiree and Apple Music posted pics from the party and the performance..@theweeknd takes the #MetGala stage!-- -- --@voguemagazine @metmuseum pic.twitter.com/lbvhyZSzoL Apple Music (@AppleMusic) May 3, 2016
